@startuml PTaaS_Engagement

' ============================================
' SEQUENCE DIAGRAM: PTaaS Engagement
' Bug Bounty and Its Simulation Platform
' ============================================

title Penetration Testing as a Service (PTaaS) - Sequence Diagram

actor "Organization" as Org
participant "Organization Portal\n(Next.js)" as UI
participant "PTaaS Engine\n(FastAPI)" as PTaaS
participant "BountyMatch Engine" as Matching
participant "PostgreSQL DB" as DB
participant "Notification Service" as Notification
participant "Researcher" as Researcher
participant "MinIO Storage" as MinIO

== Create PTaaS Engagement ==
Org -> UI: Login & navigate to PTaaS
UI -> PTaaS: GET /ptaas/templates
PTaaS -> DB: Query engagement templates
DB --> PTaaS: Templates (Web App, API, Mobile, etc.)
PTaaS --> UI: Template list
UI --> Org: Display templates

Org -> UI: Select "Web Application Pentest"
Org -> UI: Fill engagement details\n{scope, duration, budget, requirements}
UI -> PTaaS: POST /ptaas/engagements\n{template, scope, duration, budget}

PTaaS -> DB: BEGIN TRANSACTION
PTaaS -> DB: INSERT engagement
PTaaS -> DB: INSERT scope details
PTaaS -> DB: INSERT requirements
DB --> PTaaS: Engagement ID: ENG-001

PTaaS -> Matching: POST /matching/find-researchers\n{skills: ["web", "api"], experience: "senior"}
Matching -> DB: Query qualified researchers
DB --> Matching: Researcher list (10 matches)
Matching --> PTaaS: Matched researchers

PTaaS -> DB: INSERT researcher invitations
PTaaS -> DB: COMMIT TRANSACTION

PTaaS -> Notification: Send invitations
Notification -> Researcher: Email: "PTaaS invitation: $5000"

PTaaS --> UI: Engagement created (ENG-001)
UI --> Org: "Engagement created! Invitations sent"

== Researcher Accepts Engagement ==
Researcher -> UI: Login & view invitations
UI -> PTaaS: GET /ptaas/invitations
PTaaS -> DB: Query researcher invitations
DB --> PTaaS: Invitation list
PTaaS --> UI: Invitations
UI --> Researcher: Display invitation details

Researcher -> UI: Accept engagement ENG-001
UI -> PTaaS: POST /ptaas/engagements/ENG-001/accept

PTaaS -> DB: BEGIN TRANSACTION
PTaaS -> DB: UPDATE invitation status = "accepted"
PTaaS -> DB: INSERT engagement_researcher
PTaaS -> DB: UPDATE engagement status = "in_progress"
PTaaS -> DB: COMMIT TRANSACTION

PTaaS -> Notification: Send acceptance notification
Notification -> Org: Email: "Researcher accepted engagement"

PTaaS --> UI: Engagement accepted
UI --> Researcher: "Engagement started! Access scope details"

== Conduct Penetration Testing ==
Researcher -> UI: Access engagement workspace
UI -> PTaaS: GET /ptaas/engagements/ENG-001/workspace
PTaaS -> DB: Query engagement details & scope
DB --> PTaaS: Workspace data
PTaaS --> UI: Workspace (scope, credentials, timeline)
UI --> Researcher: Display workspace

Researcher -> Researcher: Perform penetration testing
Researcher -> UI: Submit findings (multiple vulnerabilities)

loop For each vulnerability found
    Researcher -> UI: Create finding report
    UI -> MinIO: Upload evidence files
    MinIO --> UI: File URLs
    
    UI -> PTaaS: POST /ptaas/engagements/ENG-001/findings\n{title, severity, evidence}
    PTaaS -> DB: INSERT finding
    PTaaS -> Notification: Notify organization
    Notification -> Org: Email: "New finding: Critical SQLi"
end

== Generate Final Report ==
Researcher -> UI: Mark testing complete
Researcher -> UI: Generate final report
UI -> PTaaS: POST /ptaas/engagements/ENG-001/report/generate

PTaaS -> DB: Query all findings
DB --> PTaaS: Finding list (15 vulnerabilities)

PTaaS -> PTaaS: Generate comprehensive report\n{executive_summary, findings, recommendations}
PTaaS -> MinIO: Upload PDF report
MinIO --> PTaaS: Report URL

PTaaS -> DB: BEGIN TRANSACTION
PTaaS -> DB: UPDATE engagement status = "completed"
PTaaS -> DB: INSERT final report
PTaaS -> DB: COMMIT TRANSACTION

PTaaS -> Notification: Send completion notification
Notification -> Org: Email: "PTaaS completed - Report ready"

PTaaS --> UI: Report generated
UI --> Researcher: "Report submitted successfully"

== Organization Review & Payment ==
Org -> UI: Login & view completed engagements
UI -> PTaaS: GET /ptaas/engagements/ENG-001/report
PTaaS -> DB: Query report & findings
DB --> PTaaS: Report data
PTaaS -> MinIO: Get report PDF
MinIO --> PTaaS: PDF file
PTaaS --> UI: Report & findings
UI --> Org: Display report

Org -> UI: Review findings & report quality
Org -> UI: Approve payment
UI -> PTaaS: POST /ptaas/engagements/ENG-001/approve

PTaaS -> DB: BEGIN TRANSACTION
PTaaS -> DB: UPDATE engagement payment_status = "approved"
PTaaS -> DB: UPDATE researcher wallet
PTaaS -> DB: INSERT transaction
PTaaS -> DB: COMMIT TRANSACTION

PTaaS -> Notification: Send payment notification
Notification -> Researcher: Email: "Payment received: $5000"

PTaaS --> UI: Payment processed
UI --> Org: "Engagement completed & paid"

@enduml